{"tid":821098,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"我發現玩開難度game真係翻唔到轉頭","createTime":"2018-09-15T19:34:37.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-18T12:58:53.000Z","uid":70429,"like":23,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"01c3f5124f90881102104c9368a3ebd3b53ec43e","tid":821098,"uid":70429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-15T19:34:37.000Z","msg":"第一次接觸難度game係FC機既人間兵器(Code Name: Viper),<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/0/00/Code_Name_-_Viper_%28screen%29.png/220px-Code_Name_-_Viper_%28screen%29.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fen%2Fthumb%2F0%2F00%2FCode_Name_-_Viper_%2528screen%2529.png%2F220px-Code_Name_-_Viper_%2528screen%2529.png&h=75be8514&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n果陣我小一左右望住老豆玩,佢玩到直接丟爛個手制.<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n之後踏入gba年代,玩惡魔城,又係劇情豐富到仆街而且好多隱藏路隱藏房間既game,仲要有隱藏結局...對於充滿探索欲既小朋友來講真係好撚正.<img src=\"http://t1.baidu.com/it/u=925492234,346909511&amp;fm=20\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft1.baidu.com%2Fit%2Fu%3D925492234%2C346909511%26fm%3D20&h=93228e9f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nonline game年代..果陣唔興新手教學或者教你點打機...全部都要你自己摸索..例如征服,魔域,夢想世界,龍之谷之類,基本上d遊戲又有公會又有女玩家,江湖恩怨日日新,開紅名野外殺人又得,日日都想變強,打pvp技術大於點數既年代依然還有那麼幾年.<img src=\"http://img5.dwstatic.com/news/1302/225026402620/225026402626.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg5.dwstatic.com%2Fnews%2F1302%2F225026402620%2F225026402626.jpg&h=f9446fa0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://images.ali213.net/picfile/pic/2016/04/15/2016041531652718.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimages.ali213.net%2Fpicfile%2Fpic%2F2016%2F04%2F15%2F2016041531652718.jpg&h=04df8310&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最後可以自己搵錢買game既年代,玩darksouls...每一次贏每一次過關每一次搵到火堆既成功感可以話係爽過打J...之後再玩落hollow knight, divinity, darkest dungeon果d...屌,成個童年回憶變成高清畫質咁翻曬來.<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n因此,如今冇一款手機game可以玩超過7日...<br />\n<br />\n因為款款都好似強制捉撚住你隻手教你玩咁款..<br />\n<br />\n新手教學逼你過曬先比你正式開波果d真心直接del.<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n*同埋我發現越難玩既game d背景音樂好似越好聽,係咪心理作用?"},{"pid":"fc53a3a9f490a35cebf7bd20bf0eb31b9d42d8bb","tid":821098,"uid":80140,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-15T20:08:02.000Z","msg":"好懷念舊online game個年代<br />\n日日衝返去升Lv 吹水 感覺好close 又容易識朋友<br />\n岩傾加msn<br />\n而家住自動 全掛機 on99<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54b9082bb51582a82a378b9b3a75c9223d346885","tid":821098,"uid":80787,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-15T20:38:08.000Z","msg":"Darkest dungeon 爆機𠴱幾關啲音樂每次聽親都好撚抑壓<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46cc4a7cb96108d37f798799798e9fabb58cb96b","tid":821098,"uid":1085,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-15T20:42:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6f0543e1f91ec03d8596b33732ef136a5b08a842","tid":821098,"uid":30831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T00:12:36.000Z","msg":"SC2呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nHallow Knight真係爽 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過DLC未玩 真結局boss打唔贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d9360e16dfff2d6d208186050445f83ddd883be","tid":821098,"uid":51963,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T00:17:01.000Z","msg":"魔界村 PSP玩過未?"},{"pid":"a06daee6535165a69d3a6463f0621ca57e910fe9","tid":821098,"uid":200199,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T00:18:46.000Z","msg":"AOC<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  識玩同唔識玩簡直係天同地"},{"pid":"4ce118bcb335434737b3bbdbb9df6f708e6f1fe3","tid":821098,"uid":7042